{"tid":25393,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 － 芝士茄子肉醬千層麵","createTime":"2016-12-06T05:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T04:53:47.000Z","uid":30742,"like":90,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb03ac7b7b43bf691c186c459774ddf361623843","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/vL0zP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FvL0zP.jpg&h=fb684ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢味野我真係唔敢成日整！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為實在要落好多芝士！<br />\n好『邪惡』！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完真係好重罪惡感！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （食果時係梗係唔會覺得啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但因為上星期入左醫院做檢查，成日唔比食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直情好似靈魂出竅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放監真係唔可以虧待自己，整呢個就最正喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMy fanspage:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=vmfswHDa%2FdeqHnVAcoF6BWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=73462da1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nMy blog:<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=vmfswHDa%2FdeqHnVAcoF6BWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=063e62e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a><br />\nig: _oldlady_<br />\n芝士茄子肉醬千層麵：<a hr