墟買一盤盤（因為我種左幾包種子都發唔到芽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n乾既我都係求其買～<br />\n<br />\n我都唔係真係好識用～但落左又真係香d既<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發芽睇手神<br />\n我種刁草個盤<br />\n一次過倒左一包種落去<br />\n每次有一棵舊苗死新芽就出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我想dum想dum拖左成年<br />\n<br />\n最後我上youtube睇人點種<br />\n原來係要搵廚紙包住種紙拎去浸水(環境要暗)<br />\n浸到出芽先再轉去泥種</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前係將廚紙浸濕，放種子再入保鮮袋等佢發！<br />\n都係好難出芽，再唔係就未大就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係果實挖出後既種子就易d,好似辣椒果d<br />\n如果係包裝種子就超難種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cf6318e61bdcb45afbccf78d566b60c96dbae5","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:00:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正呀 呢個好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係幾好！又易煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06d2320c54fd461e640c51a5c45fc1c71b6b80f","tid":25393,"uid":4209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"餓撚死朕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9442e3309d0849bfeacf14f4a402adea6f1a72","tid":25393,"uid":34725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:02:48.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3e37185ce5baef7c410654c856fb754c832b334b","tid":25393,"uid":16408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:03:09.000Z","msg":"啲芝士好邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0293d24a636d403eba8aeae54d4fabd0d6d01c0e","tid":25393,"uid":33466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"茄子 芝士 肉醬<br />\n樣樣都中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67d70fe9d57b6afba8a647acf20f7ca978d0603","tid":25393,"uid":25188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:06:47.000Z","msg":"勁鍾意食!! 老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c017ad7236531c79241d8c5d8a17a9953afe6e","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲芝士好邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果可以拉絲就更正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61273f6dc95c9959b23e4fe60dbfb7acda2ee1f","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茄子 芝士 肉醬<br />\n樣樣都中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個量可以食兩餐！帶埋飯都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3459bff3a94e9cc2aae9b5955cce9398274a4237","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勁鍾意食!! 老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就要試下整喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1492a963c31ad70fdb354da8df744ceb428273f3","tid":25393,"uid":13690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"茄子同千層麵呢個配搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次見"},{"pid":"9324ee148588f725eb45e2097561837ff888f0d6","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茄子同千層麵呢個配搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次見</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74b82de5d2143023bba53b84396ab8de13e4cc9","tid":25393,"uid":4340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26839dc6c227bf1180ef49ed00a83e707118aadc","tid":25393,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;唔是好識買同用香草 有冇教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新鮮既我就係花墟買一盤盤（因為我種左幾包種子都發唔到芽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n乾既我都係求其買～<br />\n<br />\n我都唔係真係好識用～但落左又真係香d既<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n發芽睇手神<br />\n我種刁草個盤<br />\n一次過倒左一包種落去<br />\n每次有一棵舊苗死新芽就出<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我想dum想dum拖左成年<br />\n<br />\n最後我上youtube睇人點種<br />\n原來係要搵廚紙包住種紙拎去浸水(環境要暗)<br />\n浸到出芽先再轉去泥種&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n我之前係將廚紙浸濕，放種子再入保鮮袋等佢發！<br />\n都係好難出芽，再唔係就未大就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係果實挖出後既種子就易d,好似辣椒果d<br />\n如果係包裝種子就超難種<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我棵刁草都有三四個月<br />\n仲係keep住兩三星期就爆一棵苗出來<br />\n真係唔知要等幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有買外國種子易種啲<br />\n發芽率高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72139c5ff853aa151c0ae85f033d2204af92b0b","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;唔是好識買同用香草 有冇教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新鮮既我就係花墟買一盤盤（因為我種左幾包種子都發唔到芽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n乾既我都係求其買～<br />\n<br />\n我都唔係真係好識用～但落左又真係香d既<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;gt;<br />\n發芽睇手神<br />\n我種刁草個盤<br />\n一次過倒左一包種落去<br />\n每次有一棵舊苗死新芽就出<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我想dum想dum拖左成年<br />\n<br />\n最後我上youtube睇人點種<br />\n原來係要搵廚紙包住種紙拎去浸水(環境要暗)<br />\n浸到出芽先再轉去泥種&amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n我之前係將廚紙浸濕，放種子再入保鮮袋等佢發！<br />\n都係好難出芽，再唔係就未大就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係果實挖出後既種子就易d,好似辣椒果d<br />\n如果係包裝種子就超難種<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我棵刁草都有三四個月<br />\n仲係keep住兩三星期就爆一棵苗出來<br />\n真係唔知要等幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有買外國種子易種啲<br />\n發芽率高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個星期六都想出花墟望下！<br />\n呢個天氣岩種！<br />\n我種迷迭香死左好多次，係呢種到而家仲未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535a4a781b820244d6bcbd89ca6e847f0b981a37","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a694c3343a67611ccb018e80a70a542eb1c188","tid":25393,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"老娘<br />\n捨得嫁比我未"},{"pid":"98d769926938656969bcf4d914153e8c99165928","tid":25393,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:27:25.000Z","msg":"極邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd121a5fb00ee8bb3ef13128fed42b3220bd5210","tid":25393,"uid":2211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b732aa407d7f26ce3dd85cd9f8338e29319ee0e4","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>極邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係食左一角仔ja其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18db253f031a2ac02f4acd176d1357fc6c95e7ca","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:09:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘<br />\n捨得嫁比我未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efff2a2ea085f8c215e3e52792d10ce9a1b12d8c","tid":25393,"uid":1275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:10:39.000Z","msg":"老娘你咪仲邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236ad1938025f7c23d4cc9f73a23eb5b36fdf79a","tid":25393,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"老娘用埋晒新假期果啲極邪惡字眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但老娘是最好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b1ea611ab02d6242d8e81553c86341330c3d1f","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘用埋晒新假期果啲極邪惡字眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但老娘是最好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我己經唔敢放係標題喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05504e8ae29aa2317d92391bbefd0d989d0e011","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘你咪仲邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我不嬲重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f058310ab9f342473ac11e7e1cc99eeb032f0102","tid":25393,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:29:14.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b65b633aa475a018955f053f48b7a527ecef4d","tid":25393,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝"},{"pid":"0d5961000cfc62ecf6f57dfc2b5a30c2aa7a2fec","tid":25393,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:08:37.000Z","msg":"普通肉醬意粉個醬係咪都咁上下<br />\n<br />\n我成日用d現成意粉醬唔係幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd1a39ba7acedd4199c906dee80fde206afd571","tid":25393,"uid":58615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:43:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8d79c9fc817fe96ca3c3180ddbdf51ccebabb0af","tid":25393,"uid":9024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:01:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquot